      "text": "UserAccount\n     user_id\n     username\n     password\n     name\n     DateOfBirth\n     shortBio\n     EmailId\n     PhoneNumber\n     Location: <Lat/Long>\n     pictures: [S3Link]\n     prompts: [{id, value}]\n     LastModifiedTimestamp\n     CreationTimestamp\n     maxLocation\n     AgeStartRange: \n     AgeEndRange:\n",
